verbose_text: As shown in XREF_FIG, each of these treatments did not lower Ang II levels in the SHRSP brains compared with SHRSP-Veh, however, Ald levels were significantly downregulated in SHRSP-Los6 and SHRSP-Los16 at 10 and 20 weeks compared with SHRSP-Veh, and remained low in SHRSP-Los16 up to 40 weeks (XREF_FIG).
